harvest of vegetables and other foodstuffs during the summer 
because of difficult weather conditions later in the year 
it said the increases for agriculture ministry workers in 
grains vegetables and citrus fruits will be 30 percent in the city 
of havana and surrounding havana province and 20 percent elsewhere 
in cuba 
