the directory of experts authorities and spokespersons 
offers to fill the void 
the 198788 directory the fourth annual edition provides in 
its 384 yellow pages an encyclopedia of sources of fact and opinion 
on subjects ranging from aids to zoological parks the sources 
range from serious experts to whimsical organizations 
subscribers to what is subtitled the talk show guest 
directory include the major tv networks magazines newspapers 
and the us bureaus of foreign publications and news agencies 
this new edition has been written from scratch after directly 
