mercantile exchange in response to the international energy 
agencys prediction of rising world demand 
in its monthly report the group predicted a 19 percent 
increase in global oil demand this year compared to an increase of 
145 percent last year said bob baker an analyst in new york with 
prudentialbache securities inc 
